=head1 TEST PROCEDURE

=begin html
<PRE>
                    
 (1) MN(NUT#) moves from Link0 to LinkX.
                    
       HA0    NUTX      R1      R2     CN0
        |       |       |       |       |
        |       | <---- |       |       | 1.Router Advertisement
        |       |       |       |       |
        | <---- |       |       |       | 2.Binding Update
        | ----> |       |       |       | 3.Binding Acknowledgement
        |       |       |       |       |
        |       |       |       |       | 4.(wait)
        |       |       |       |       |
        | <---- |       |       |       | 5.Binding Update
        | ----> |       |       |       | 6.Binding Acknowledgement
        |       |       |       |       |
                    
 (2) MN(NUT#) moves from LinkX to LinkY.
                    
       HA0    NUTY      R1      R2     CN0
        |       |       |       |       |
        |       | <------------ |       | 7.Router Advertisement
        |       |       |       |       |
        |       | ----> |       |       | 8.Neighbor Solicitation (NUD)
        |       |       |       |       | 9.(no reply)
        |       |       |       |       |
        | <---- |       |       |       | 10.Binding Update
        | ----> |       |       |       | 11.Binding Acknowledgement
        |       |       |       |       |
                    
 (1) MN(NUT#) moves from Link0 to LinkX.
        1. Send Router Advertisement. (R1 -> R1_allnode_multi)
        2. Receive Binding Update. (NUTX -> HA0)
        3. Send Binding Acknowledgement. (HA0 -> NUTX)
        4. (wait)
            # Wait during a maximum of the lifetime in the Binding Acknowledgement[3].
        5. Receive Binding Update. (NUTX -> HA0)
        6. Send Binding Acknowledgement. (HA0 -> NUTX)
                    
 (2) MN(NUT#) moves from LinkX to LinkY.
        7. Send Router Advertisement. (R2 -> R2_allnode_multi)
        8. Receive Neighbor Solicitation (NUD). (NUTX -> R1)
        9. (no reply)
            # Wait during a maximum of 3 seconds(RFC2461).
       10. Receive Binding Update. (NUTY -> HA0)
       11. Send Binding Acknowledgement. (HA0 -> NUTY)
                    
<UL>
<LI><B><FONT SIZE="+1">In the case of Real Home Link</FONT></B>
</UL>
                    
 (3) MN(NUT#) returns to its Home Link(moves from LinkY to Link0).
                    
       HA0    NUT0      R1      R2     CN0
        |       |       |       |       |
        | ----> |       |       |       | 12.Router Advertisement
        |       |       |       |       |
        |       | ------------> |       | 13.Neighbor Solicitation (NUD)
        |       |       |       |       | 14.(no reply:3seconds)
        |       |       |       |       |
        | <---- |       |       |       | 15.Binding Update
        | ----> |       |       |       | 16.Binding Acknowledgement
        |       |       |       |       |
        | <---- |       |       |       | 17.Neighbor Advertisement
        |       |       |       |       |
                    
 (3) MN(NUT#) returns to its Home Link(moves from LinkY to Link0).
       12. Send Router Advertisement. (HA0 -> HA0_allnode_multi)
       13. Receive Neighbor Solicitation (NUD). (NUTY -> R2)
       14. (no reply)
            # Wait during a maximum of  3 seconds(RFC2461).
       15. Receive Binding Update. (NUT0 -> HA0)
       16. Send Binding Acknowledgement. (HA0 -> NUT0)
       17. Receive Neighbor Advertisement. (NUT0 -> NUT0_allnode_multi)
</PRE>

